Edit your Appointment with <%= @appointment.service_provider.company_name %>
<%= form_for @appointment do |f| %>
<%= f.hidden_field :service_provider_id, value: @appointment.service_provider.id %>
Who's the appointment for? <%= f.collection_select :pet_id, @current_owner.pets, :id, :name %><br>
What's the appointment for?<%= f.collection_select :service_type, @appointment.service_provider.service_types, :to_s, :to_s %><br>
When is the appointment for?<%= f.datetime_field :date %><br>
How long is the appointment for? <%= f.number_field :duration %> hours<br>
<%= f.submit %>
<% end %>